text: Kennelbach is a municipality in the district of Bregenz in the Austrian state of Vorarlberg. As of 2016, it is the operational headquarters of the sporting goods manufacturer Head, along with Amsterdam, the corporate headquarters.Head official website == Twin cities == * Scurelle, Italy == References == == Other websites == * Official website of Kennelbach Category:Settlements in Vorarlberg
